  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section>
    <div class="mission">
      <div class="eyebrow">Why I do this</div>
      <blockquote>
        "As long as you're growing something you care about and giving back to your community, you're
        building in the right direction. I started GlassBee after years of growing businesses myself,
        feeling the growing pains firsthand of trying to establish an online presence while staying focused
